'''Bribb juice''' was a drink served at [[Panky's]]. [[Anakin Skywalker/Legends|Anakin Skywalker]] tasted it on his first assignment as a [[Padawan/Legends|Padawan]] and since then and also on [[27 BBY/Legends|27 BBY]] he had ordered it on every occasion, no matter if it matched the meal or not. [[Lorana Jinzler]] also enjoyed it.<ref name="Outbound Flight">[[Outbound Flight (novel)|''Outbound Flight'']]</ref>

